{"tid":582721,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"G奶當街被咬一口！　熊熊嚇到尖叫：來得太突然","createTime":"2018-03-06T12:03:56.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-06T17:48:01.000Z","uid":1121,"like":3,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"2f31f613b4583210a39e3dc2180dbcfb34a9ea25","tid":582721,"uid":1121,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-06T12:03:56.000Z","msg":"「G奶女神」熊熊（卓毓彤）不只有前凸後翹的好身材，平常也會學習不同才藝增進自己，近來迷上潛水的她，和好友王晴準備走去上課的路途中，巧遇一隻虎斑貓，喵星人意外超黏人，整個頭一直在她的肚皮上磨蹭，沒想到，下秒胸部被突襲咬了一口，嚇得她放聲尖叫：「意外來得太突然！」<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/3147/d3147683.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F3147%2Fd3147683.jpg&h=b8b2ebd5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲▼熊熊路邊巧遇小貓咪。（圖／翻攝自熊熊IG）<br />\n<a href=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/3147/d3147682.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F3147%2Fd3147682.jpg&d=0YmnJd%2BfqxM%2FGufa1yEzKcPrXSGIZiPsBFv3mRhlVuk%3D&h=3456a703\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/3147/d3147682.jpg</a>"},{"pid":"3a1bd0341ccea2c7e25196cf523dcbeaae91c91c","tid":582721,"uid":1121,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-06T12:04:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/3147/d3147682.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F3147%2Fd3147682.jpg&h=7418eb4b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"947e163cf06d37a6a8645b29d358b1b4f0e4464a","tid":582721,"uid":1121,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-06T12:04:57.000Z","msg":"影片中，可以看到熊熊穿著貼身條紋T恤，完美包覆豐滿上圍，寬鬆剪裁露出漂亮的鎖骨線條，搭配熱褲展現白皙美腿，從頭到腳都讓人難以移開視線，就連貓咪也無法抵擋她的魅力，就在她低頭撫摸小貓、任由它磨蹭時，喵星人居然無預警張嘴輕咬了一口胸部，瞬間大叫，止不住笑聲說：「虎斑貓都這麼親人嗎？」<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/3147/d3147684.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F3147%2Fd3147684.jpg&h=b277e2cc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲▼喵星人磨蹭到一半，突襲熊熊胸部還咬了一口。（圖／翻攝自熊熊IG）<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/3147/d3147685.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F3147%2Fd3147685.jpg&h=7edde252&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"04b2ec8c2f066b96fd3608cd552e0c1c1f0dddb8","tid":582721,"uid":1121,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-06T12:05:29.000Z","msg":"畫面曝光後，粉絲無一不表示羨慕，狂虧貓咪：「好幸福呀」、「以後也想當貓」、「放開那女孩！」但也有人注意到熊熊笑起來的樣子，真的很迷人，「妳笑起來真好看！」尤其胸部被偷襲的那瞬間，害羞大笑的模樣，融化了不少網友，也成為影片的另一亮點。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/3147/d3147686.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F3147%2Fd3147686.jpg&h=f052e5b1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲熊熊被貓咪突如其來的舉動嚇到尖叫。（圖／翻攝自熊熊IG）<br />\n<br />\n此外，熊熊也透露，這次去菲律賓度假回來，在當地換穿比基尼恣意地曬太陽，幸好都沒有曬黑，「太佩服自己了。」只是天氣忽冷忽熱，害她感冒都不見好轉，聲音一直是沙啞狀態。"},{"pid":"edccfc3d585e543b8114d683cabadb4784b2de86","tid":582721,"uid":57835,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-06T12:05:48.000Z","msg":"老啦又矮"},{"pid":"92115e78e42583c1ae31f5dbaae059fe2dd092c6","tid":582721,"uid":8957,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-06T12:06:11.000Z","msg":"後來貓貓有冇中毒身亡<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ？"},{"pid":"b57f50df58bdbd0f9c95b44dacbac3d199c87262","tid":582721,"uid":63302,"like":5,"dislike":5,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-06T12:06:39.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"577c331e1719fbee89b8aff5403c861a5a050f02","tid":582721,"uid":1121,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-06T12:06:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://www.worldofbuzz.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/giphy-5.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.worldofbuzz.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F02%2Fgiphy-5.gif&h=19c15df5&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"afba955329a034d203551bb8aeb491a4452e1474","tid":582721,"uid":1121,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"edccfc3d585e543b8114d683cabadb4784b2de86","tid":582721,"uid":57835,"